{"tid":2293871,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過喺餐廳食飯遇到一啲好窩心嘅事？","createTime":"2020-11-20T14:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T14:47:11.000Z","uid":134103,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"844793717027ba78967449ea1e7e3f92acc6ba7f","tid":2293871,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"今晚本身約咗朋友食飯，不過俾人放飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我唯有自己食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嗌咗個青咖哩雜菜飯，諗住話青咖哩應該唔辣，點知辣到我係咁標眼水同流鼻涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知食食下，啱啱幫我落單嗰位侍應姐姐突然行埋嚟，放低咗一件蛋糕同一疊紙巾，我心諗做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「先生你好呀，呢個係我哋餐廳最受歡迎嘅藍梅芝士蛋糕，係請你食㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n「下？」<br />\n<br />\n「唔好咁唔開心啦，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」佢講完之後向我點一點頭，跟住就行開咗<br />\n<br />\n我諗返轉頭，今日係happy friday，周圍都一pair pair或者係成班朋友去食飯，得我係自己一丁友，又一路食一路抹眼淚，佢可能係以為失戀/失業/壓力好大，所以想鼓勵下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係失戀嘅時候都冇人對我咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />估唔到食辣嘢食到標眼水反而有陌生人請我食蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰種感覺就好似《食神》入面火雞姐喺史提芬周俾人打咗獲之後請佢食叉燒飯咁，真係好~好~味~呀~<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知侍應姐姐你睇唔睇到呢個po，我想再同你講多聲多謝，多謝你請我食蛋糕，但係其實我真係冇唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />順便我想你同個廚反映下，個青咖哩真係好辣，我諗爭少少就到譚仔大辣，如果有得揀辣度就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708a2b6acd7143238b77813c531f4ff1e4cdcf37","tid":2293871,"uid":337986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"樓主靚仔？"},{"pid":"f7c6befa2c540cf7b6d7d16f6dd9f785bc657c75","tid":2293871,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"708a2b6acd7143238b77813c531f4ff1e4cdcf37","tid":2293871,"uid":337986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"樓主靚仔？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"肥矮柒毒，bmi過30<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e43c80bc9cf03fd1b2f277be0a0b95c6dd9c3a7","tid":2293871,"uid":134103,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"唔使問我間餐廳叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n非PR公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係想分享下香港其實仲有餐廳係好有人情味，特別係黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acc496a837ff1e788bfb9910be77143a6d86cd9","tid":2293871,"uid":210742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b11b74ca833383c77f95a3d4f430438750e0cc","tid":2293871,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2acc496a837ff1e788bfb9910be77143a6d86cd9","tid":2293871,"uid":210742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:38:13.000Z","msg":"笑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好Warm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90b6a9173000285d50c0b657962e1f092067a3b","tid":2293871,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e43c80bc9cf03fd1b2f277be0a0b95c6dd9c3a7","tid":2293871,"uid":134103,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"唔使問我間餐廳叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n非PR公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係想分享下香港其實仲有餐廳係好有人情味，特別係黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"個人經驗（標榜）黃店好撚難食⋯"},{"pid":"a3ce6631f336979ec2f1bc7d1570178e873ad77d","tid":2293871,"uid":24317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e43c80bc9cf03fd1b2f277be0a0b95c6dd9c3a7","tid":2293871,"uid":134103,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"唔使問我間餐廳叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n非PR公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係想分享下香港其實仲有餐廳係好有人情味，特別係黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"黃店就開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"