 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"咩意思呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好辣吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e4582f503f347d75e4326db915a6ddefea4967","tid":2293871,"uid":126226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 剩係試過食拉麵食到上氣唔接下氣咁..之後有職員見到 <br />\n無啦啦比杯野飲同紙巾我~<br />\n<br />\nPS.我就係鐘意食到頭暈既感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19b4d9109b9cb91be82e35a25ec31b50d0295ae","tid":2293871,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"669a6a0d9133bbadea25730b9927e6453c6cf3da","tid":2293871,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:40:34.000Z","msg":"人間有情"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"係，香港其實好有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf66c8839423c319174d586000c0e5ef346e36c","tid":2293871,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33e4582f503f347d75e4326db915a6ddefea4967","tid":2293871,"uid":126226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 剩係試過食拉麵食到上氣唔接下氣咁..之後有職員見到 <br />\n無啦啦比杯野飲同紙巾我~<br />\n<br />\nPS.我就係鐘意食到頭暈既感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"